WEBVTT

00:03:57.427 --> 00:04:00.664
The media had made him famous.

00:04:02.468 --> 00:04:05.962
But my firstborn son, Alex,

00:04:05.986 --> 00:04:07.311
a hero,

00:04:08.134 --> 00:04:11.837
was absent from those initial reports.

